This is meant as a term to what rumours or news is going around on the Internet, in businesses, on the street or just in general people's social lives.

It can also be meant as a way of what people are listening into.  Whether it be just happen to be listening to someone's conversation or what Spies may do in Fictional stories.

Other such phrases to describe are 'word is on the street...' or 'rumour is...'